"Oh God!" Teltoli suddenly remember that the other bot (Aerotaur) was 
still out there!

Hastily she got WindLord's attention, and asked him "That other bot, 
that was with you, is he okay? Oohh and can we land soon, my heads 
starting to feel dizzy" She said the last bit weakly, holding her 
head between her hands to try stay awake, as the tranq was weighing 
her eyelids down with sleep.
